# Rebuilding Showcases: UI-UX Pro Max Integration

This plan detail the full reconstruction of the Claw Ecosystem websites using the **UI-UX Pro Max** reasoning engine and design standards.

## 📐 Master Design System ([design-system/MASTER.md](file:///Users/mkazi/claw-ecosystem/design-system/MASTER.md))
- **Global Pattern**: Ecosystem-as-Platform.
- **Global Tone**: Professional, high-intelligence, dark-themed (OLED optimization).
- **Core Typography**: Inter (Sans) for UI, JetBrains Mono for Technical/Code.
- **Core Principles**: No emojis for icons (Lucide SVG), `cursor-pointer` everywhere, 300ms transitions.

## 📜 Evolution & Lineage Story
- **Concept**: OpenClaw is the "Genesis Node". All other agents are specialized forks or evolutions designed for specific environmental constraints (Edge, Per-Project, mission-critical).
- **Portal Upgrade**: Implement a **"Lineage Tree"** visualization in the main portal using SVG paths that "branch" from OpenClaw to the 4 alternatives.
- **OpenClaw Status**: Labeled as **[MAINHEAD / GENESIS]**.

## ✨ Premium Interactivity (UI-UX Pro Max)
- **Data Flow**: Use CSS `stroke-dashoffset` animations on the lineage paths to simulate live data moving between agents.
- **Parallax Layers**: Implement deep-scroll parallax on agent cards.
- **Micro-Interactions**:
  - HSL-shifting glow on hover.
  - "Scanline" reveal transition when entering an agent portal.
  - Dynamic "System Pulse" (The heart of the ecosystem).
- **Interactive Timeline**: A scroll-triggered event log showing the birth of each agent.

## 📦 Content Enrichment (Original Repo Deep-Dive)
- **Nanobot**: Include the "HR Campaign" logic snippets and Notion-sync field mappings.
- **NanoClaw**: Detail the "Swarm Configuration" files for specific coding/research teams.
- **OpenClaw**: Integrate the full **RALPH v2** protocol documentation and "60-Project Portfolio" management stats.
- **PicoClaw**: Show the "Heartbeat" cron definitions and thermal throttling logic.
- **ZeroClaw**: Display the "Audit Gate" verification steps and Rust memory-safety proof points.

## 🌐 Publishing & Showcase Phase
- **Repository Strategy**: Implement the Hub-and-Spoke Monorepo for unified ecosystem management.
- **GitHub Pages**: Configure automated deployment for all 6 interactive showcases ([index.html](file:///Users/mkazi/claw-ecosystem/index.html) files).
- **Social Optimization**: Set up Open Graph tags and Social Preview images for premium link sharing.
- **README Hub**: Create a high-fidelity root README with Lucide icons and internal lineage mapping.

## ✅ Pre-Delivery Checklist (UI-UX Pro Max)
- [ ] SVG-only icons (no emojis).
- [ ] Hover states on all buttons/links.
- [ ] Smooth transitions on all interactions.
- [ ] Full responsiveness (Mobile to 4K).
- [ ] Accessible color contrast.
